<h1>free-home-Bridge</h1>

<p>Free@home is using XMPP for homeautomatisation this bridge trys to simplyfy the communication between systems like openhab and other open source systems</p>

<h2>Build</h2>

<p>To build the Serve maven and a jdk 1.8 is required. 
Just Clone and run maven</p>

<p>```</p>

<pre><code>git clone https://github.com/hasisunkid/free-home-Bridge.git
cd free-home-bridge
mvn install
</code></pre>

<p>```</p>

<h2>Configuration</h2>

<p>there is a template configuration file <code>config.cfg</code> to adapt it to your environment pleas edit it.</p>

<h2>Installation</h2>

<p>Just copy the jar file and the /lib directory to your prevered location.</p>

<h2>Start</h2>

<p>```</p>

<pre><code>java -Xmx20m -jar FreeHomeBridge-0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar config.cfg
</code></pre>

<p>```</p>

